# System Resource Monitor CLI

## ğŸŒ Overview

A powerful Python CLI tool to monitor and log system resources in real-time.

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ“Š Monitor system resources:
  - CPU usage
  - Memory consumption
  - Network I/O
  - GPU metrics (temperature, memory usage, load)
- ğŸ•’ Customizable monitoring interval
- â±ï¸ Optional time-limited monitoring
- ğŸ’¾ Export data in CSV or JSON formats
